{"tid":2283754,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國泰大裁員︱十年經驗一朝清零 空服員落地再出發","createTime":"2020-11-12T21:20:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-13T03:51:41.000Z","uid":130626,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"4c33ed25f987489c41d20950e368b6a2614215da","tid":2283754,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T21:20:58.000Z","msg":"近年投資期油失利，今年再遭武漢肺炎疫情夾擊，一直被視為「香港名牌」的國泰航空，上月一口氣裁減5,300名香港員工，大量空中服務員首當其衝，正式告別天空從此「落地」。《蘋果》訪問了3名年資逾十年的空姐、空少，有人「馬死落地行」邊做兼職邊搵工，有人早作準備有穩定炒散保障生計，亦有人「待價而沽」希望維持work-life balance。有人力資源顧問認同空服員應變強有優勢，但提醒市道仍然不景，太多類似資歷人才湧現，市場難完全消化。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201113/EHIILUBZIBEBXB5DUY3KOPR6RE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201113%2FEHIILUBZIBEBXB5DUY3KOPR6RE%2F&d=K%2BViKRLCts5CIle5BUc%2BylDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=0181005e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201113%2FEHIILUBZIBEBXB5DUY3KOPR6RE%2F&h=a439fc8d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201113/EHIILUBZIBEBXB5DUY3KOPR6RE/</a>"},{"pid":"c175dc50e7222b907047e5ee2bcbf7d8814104be","tid":2283754,"uid":355064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T21:21:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f8dfedd40e3528c4455b0ead863dc04563b02ab","tid":2283754,"uid":284432,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T21:26:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8e7afe5d8c8fd01134d07d8d4ed79e566d69cedc","tid":2283754,"uid":19196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T21:36:28.000Z","msg":"煲底市集 老闆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c086e7be23e6f1868b653e4f49e2a06de2bc1ce2","tid":2283754,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T23:01:16.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"bdd3491c2a92d4f747a0d91ce0b44c7c213200ee","tid":2283754,